body_html: @allenlavoie On Ubuntu 16.04, it seems to be treated more like an error rather than a warning. I seem to recall that in the issue linked above that several on MacOS stated their code still runs after throwing the warning, but at least one person mentioned that on Ubuntu their code wouldn't run after throwing this warning. The latter is the case which is happening to me.
